llm_judge_prompt_template.user_template:
请根据 rubric_v2 评估下面 inference QA。

case_id: {case_id}
qa_index: {qa_index}
question: {question}
expected_answer_or_reference_answer: {expected_answer}
candidate_model_answer: {candidate_answer}
diagnosis_opinion: {diagnosis_opinion}
mr_findings: {mr_findings}
ground_truth_labels: {ground_truth_labels}

输出严格 JSON，字段必须包含：question_id, case_id, qa_index, matched_rule_ids, question_intent, ground_truth_core, extracted_model_conclusion, required_elements, matched_elements, contradictions, verdict, correct, needs_manual_review, reason。
